        &amp;lt;line x1=&amp;quot;9&amp;quot; y1=&amp;quot;21&amp;quot; x2=&amp;quot;9&amp;quot; y2=&amp;quot;9&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/line&amp;gt;
      &amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;h3&amp;gt;Page Templates&amp;lt;/h3&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Standard page layouts for common use cases such as dashboards, forms, and landing pages.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;
