    &amp;lt;h3&amp;gt;Email Support&amp;lt;/h3&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Contact our support team directly for help with implementation issues or questions about the design system.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;a href=&amp;quot;/support/contact/&amp;quot; class=&amp;quot;channel-link&amp;quot;&amp;gt;Contact Support →&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;
