    &amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Submit bug reports, feature requests, and contribute to the design system code repository.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;a href=&amp;quot;https://github.com/enterprise-design-system&amp;quot; class=&amp;quot;channel-link&amp;quot;&amp;gt;View Repository →&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;
