      &amp;lt;p class=&amp;quot;text-[var(--color-text-muted)] flex-grow&amp;quot;&amp;gt;Our color palette system, including primary and secondary colors, semantic colors, neutrals, and usage guidelines.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;
